text: ENAD Ayiou Dometiou FC is a Cypriot football club based in Ayios Dhometios, Nicosia. Founded in 1957, it played in the second, third and fourth divisions. The team dissolved after 1993 and reactive at 2013. The team is part of the sports club ENAD Ayiou Dometiou. ==References== Category:Football clubs in Cyprus Category:Association football clubs established in 1937 Category:1937 establishments in Cyprus
